    VOLUME OF US STOCK AND BOND ISSUES
 ------------------------------------------
                           Proceeds
Year                     (Dollars bn)
 ------------------------------------------
1987                         277
1988                         279
1989                         310
1990                         314
1991                         590
1992                         857
1993                       1,063
 ------------------------------------------
Source: Securities Data
 ------------------------------------------
</TEXT>
